2025-04-23 09:51:25 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1745401885,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"185.97.16.173","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/135.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10797,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"10795","cat_id":"4","nick":"ordons","content":"Da si\u0119 to rozwi\u0105za\u0107, ale wszystko zale\u017cy od tego, gdzie mo\u017cna zamontowa\u0107 jednostk\u0119 zewn\u0119trzn\u0105 \u2013 mo\u017ce by\u0107 na elewacji, na dachu albo w innym pomieszczeniu, je\u015bli uk\u0142ad na to pozwala. Warto odezwa\u0107 si\u0119 do kogo\u015b, kto to montuje na co dzie\u0144 \u2013 np. przez https:\/\/klimatyzacja-rzeszow.pl\/. Tam mo\u017cna opisa\u0107 sytuacj\u0119 i dosta\u0107 konkretn\u0105 odpowied\u017a, czy si\u0119 da, i je\u015bli tak, to jak. Cz\u0119sto s\u0105 rozwi\u0105zania, o kt\u00f3rych samemu trudno by by\u0142o pomy\u015ble\u0107.\r\nKlima Podkarpacie\r\nAdres: Architekt\u00f3w 12, 35-082 Rzesz\u00f3w\r\nTelefon: 576 936 900","create_date":"2025-04-23 09:51:25","modify_date":"2025-04-23 09:51:25","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2764079},"entity_changes":false}
